---
import BaseLayout from "../components/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---
<BaseLayout>
  <Hero
    home
    kicker="Full-stack Builder · AICoding · Independent Apps"
    title="MrFung"
    zh="全栈开发者，AICoding 实践者，独立产品打磨者。把工程能力、产品直觉和耐力运动里的长期主义放在一起，做真实能用、能持续维护的工具。"
    en="Full-stack builder, AICoding practitioner, and independent product maker. I combine engineering, product taste, and endurance-sport discipline to build useful tools that can be maintained for the long run."
  >
    <div class="mf-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="/billloopr/">BillLoopr</a>
      <a class="button" href="/about/">关于 / About</a>
    </div>
  </Hero>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>产品与项目 / Apps & Projects</h2>
        <p>产品、支持、隐私和内容入口集中展示，适合用户和 App Store 审核快速找到需要的信息。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Billable Time</small>
            <h3>BillLoopr</h3>
            <p>独立工作者使用的计费工时、项目记录和发票准备工具。</p>
            <p>Billable time tracking, project records, and invoice preparation for independent professionals.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/billloopr/">打开 / Open</a>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Privacy</small>
            <h3>隐私政策 / Privacy Policy</h3>
            <p>说明本地存储、导出分享、支持请求和数据删除方式。</p>
            <p>Explains local storage, exports, support requests, and data deletion.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/billloopr/privacy/">查看 / View</a>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Support</small>
            <h3>支持 / Support</h3>
            <p>应用支持邮箱、常见帮助主题和 App Store 审核所需入口。</p>
            <p>Support email, common help topics, and App Store review information.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/billloopr/support/">获取支持 / Get Support</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="portrait">
          <img src="/assets/img/MrFung.jpg" alt="MrFung portrait">
        </div>
        <div class="bio">
          <h2>全栈开发、AICoding，以及山野里的长期主义。</h2>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>我关注全栈开发、AICoding、独立产品和真实工作流，也喜欢把越野跑、马拉松和水上运动里的节奏感带回到产品打磨里。</p>
            <p>I focus on full-stack development, AICoding, independent products, and practical workflows. Trail running, marathons, and paddleboarding shape how I think about pace, resilience, and craft.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-grid">
            <div class="metric"><strong>ITRA 430</strong><span>越野跑积分 / Trail running index</span></div>
            <div class="metric"><strong>马拉松大众二级</strong><span>Marathon Amateur Level 2</span></div>
            <div class="metric"><strong>有为青年</strong><span>Purpose-driven young builder</span></div>
            <div class="metric"><strong>红十字救护员</strong><span>Red Cross first aider</span></div>
            <div class="metric"><strong>越野跑</strong><span>Trail running</span></div>
            <div class="metric"><strong>划桨板</strong><span>Paddleboarding</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>内容整理中 / Writing Reset</h2>
        <p>原来的旧博客已经下线，后续会用新的结构整理全栈、AICoding、独立产品和运动实践。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>旧文章已移除</h3>
          <p>不再保留早期零散文章。新的内容会以更清楚的专题方式重新发布。</p>
          <p><a href="/archives/">查看归档状态</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Old posts removed</h3>
          <p>Older posts have been removed. Future writing will be reorganized around clearer topics.</p>
          <p><a href="/archives/">View archive status</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
